	</div>
</div></div><div class="vc_tta-panel" id="1467764655119-2034148e-46c3" data-vc-content=".vc_tta-panel-body"><div class="vc_tta-panel-heading"><h4 class="vc_tta-panel-title vc_tta-controls-icon-position-left"><a href="#1467764655119-2034148e-46c3" data-vc-accordion data-vc-container=".vc_tta-container"><span class="vc_tta-title-text">Awards, Honors and Memberships </span><i class="vc_tta-controls-icon vc_tta-controls-icon-chevron"></i></a></h4></div><div class="vc_tta-panel-body">
